  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Recovery support to flood victims in Nepal</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The torrential rain from 12-15 Aug 2017 created massive floods and several landslides in 26 districts throughout the country. As per govt data,  the flood caused 126 deaths, 50 missing and many people got severe injuries.  Due to  rain  12733 households displaced losing their property in west Nepal &amp; they are in critical state. They are immensely in need of relief supports like food grains, temporary shelter, blankets, potable water, clothing, medicines, education materials of children.</narrative>
  </description>
